\boxed{Ahom}

The **Ahom** ethnic group formed an army at **Bilpam** (also known as **Bilpama**), which served as their headquarters during their rule in the Ahom Kingdom (1228–1826) in present-day Assam, India. The term "Bilpam" refers to the royal residence and military command center of the Ahom dynasty.
